Jeanne Goupil https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeanne_Goupil 0 Jeanne Goupil (born April 4, 1950) is a French television and film actress from Soisy-sous-Montmorency who known for the Don't Deliver Us from Evil (1971), Cookies (1975) and The Grocer's Son (2007).
